CustomField.formula: IF(Follow_Up_Rating_Desc__c = 0 && Rating_Exemption_Granted__c = true, "No rating available", IF(Follow_Up_Rating_Desc__c = 1, "Significant Improvement Needed", IF(Follow_Up_Rating_Desc__c = 2, "Improvement Needed", IF(Follow_Up_Rating_Desc__c = 3, "Acceptable", IF(Follow_Up_Rating_Desc__c = 4, "Good", IF(Follow_Up_Rating_Desc__c = 5, "Excellent", "No rating available" ))))))
